                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    langAttribute="none"
                                    text="&lt;p>Throughout the season, Striking Out Cancer will be featured across MLB platforms, including MLB&amp;nbsp;Network&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;MLB digital and social channels.&amp;nbsp;The&amp;nbsp;initiative and its impact will also be spotlighted during some of the league’s most visible moments, including the MLB All-Star Game&amp;nbsp;presented by Mastercard, MLB at Field of Dreams&amp;nbsp;and the MLB Wild Card Series.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>With baseball’s massive platform and AbbVie’s leadership in oncology, the campaign creates a rare intersection of&amp;nbsp;&lt;b>science, sport, and story&lt;/b>&amp;nbsp;by turning strikeouts into symbols of awareness and hope.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
